article_title: Fire breaks out at Gunner's Oyster Bar
article_text:
Fire crews were called Sunday night to a structure fire that broke out at Gunner's Oyster Bar in Vernon.

The fire broke out around 9 p.m. Sunday. At this time fire officials have not stated the cause of the fire or if anyone was injured.

We will bring you more information as it becomes available.
